Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive agents are pleased to offer this fantastic investment opportunity in Sydney's booming north west.

The asset presents a great opportunity to acquire a secure freehold investment, currently fully occupied.

The site boasts the following attributes:

+ Fully occupied sporting complex
+ Located within the booming north west Sydney
+ Net passing rental: $719,974 p/a + GST
+ Huge opportunity to add value
+ Award winning modern design
+ Solid tenant mix with complimentary businesses
+ Fully established tenants
+ Successful operation for almost 10 years with limited vacancy
+ Strong population growth in local area
+ 2.6km* to Seven Hills Train Station
+ 2.8km* to Portico Plaza Shopping Centre

The property will be sold by way of Expressions of Interest closing Thursday, 23rd March 2017 at 4PM.

To obtain further information please contact the listing agents:

Alex Mirzaian - 0400 523 523
John Micallef - 0476 222 333

CBRE are pleased to present an opportunity to secure a modern freestanding office/warehouse in the ever popular Seven Hills Industrial precinct, offering:

- Internal clearance of up to 8.2 metres*
- 10.4* kilowatt solar panels
- Access via one (1) loading dock and ramp
- Excellent natural lighting
- Two (2) level office accommodation with full staff amenities
- Front concrete forecourt allows for excellent loading/unloading
- Fully secured site with ample parking
- Fantastic vehicular access via wide driveway
- Short and long term leases considered
- Excellent access to the M7, M2 Motorways and major arterial roads

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusively listed agents.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 1222SQM MODERN FREESTANDING OFFICE & WAREHOUSE IN SOUGHT AFTER LOCATION

- High quality, up-spec fixtures and fittings providing an excellent long term investment

- Four (4) allocated parking spaces for Unit 5
- Excellent access to the M7, M2 Motorways and major arterial roads
- The estate is now complete, and ready for occupation!

For a copy of the Contract for Sale, the Information Memorandum or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agent.
